description: A medical high school graduate came into my office today. He was incredibly tall and very cute. I have respect for medical people, especially when they work with elderly, which was the case of this young men. He used to work in health care but left because the pay wasn´t any good. After some time spent by working at factories, he decided to get a medical job again. I had a very nice place at a private sanatorium open. He was so enthusiastic about the job that he immediately agreed to please me in exchange for it. I had very specific ideas about being pleased today.He was probably the noisiest guy I have ever had in my office. I was almost afraid that the boy might get hurt. Don´t worry, he survived and left with a smile on his face.
title: Dirty Scout 72
